This system is designed for oil-and-gas EPC document control, implementing standards from:
- ARN-E-IN-00-001: All Electrical Drawing Index
- ARG-E-LO-00-006: Cable Tray and Trench Layout
- ARG-E-LO-00-007: Cable Routing Layout

